[User Locks RWA on Source Chain]
        ↓
[Proof submitted to KarrotEscrow]
        ↓ emits →
  🔁 AssetLocked(user, symbol, amount, proofHash)

[Off-chain listener or bridge backend sees event]
        ↓
Calls pxAssetMinter.mintFromLockProof(symbol, user, amount, lockProof)

        ↓
Minted: pxTSLA, pxAAPL, etc. → tradable on Pulse DEX
